law.history: Repealed 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 233, sec. 22. -- Amended 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 57, sec. 1, effective May 18, 1956. -- Amended 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 198, sec. 1. --Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 165c-8.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: License to conduct school of barbering, beauty culture -- Permit for lecture, clinic, course, etc., in cosmetology.
